# Microservicos completos sem Dapr

## 1) Objetivo
Padronizar microservicos completos sem Dapr, com resiliencia (Polly), mensageria (Kafka ou RabbitMQ), observabilidade e empacotamento Docker.

## 2) Estrutura de pastas
```
src/
  Api/
    Controllers/
    Filters/
    Program.cs
  Application/
    Commands/Queries/
    Handlers/
    DTOs/Validators/
  Domain/
    Entities/ValueObjects/Events/
    Abstractions/
  Infrastructure/
    Data/Repositories/UnitOfWork/
    Messaging/
    Observability/
  Shared/
    Contracts/
deploy/
  docker-compose.yml
  Dockerfile
tests/
  Unit/
  Integration/
```

## 3) Pacotes recomendados
- MediatR
- Polly, Polly.Extensions.Http
- Serilog.AspNetCore, Serilog.Sinks.Console
- OpenTelemetry.Extensions.Hosting
- OpenTelemetry.Instrumentation.AspNetCore, OpenTelemetry.Instrumentation.Http
- OpenTelemetry.Exporter.OpenTelemetryProtocol
- Refit (HTTP clients tipados)
- MassTransit (Kafka ou RabbitMQ)
- FluentValidation
- Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore

## 4) Configuracao (Program.cs)
```csharp
var builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder(args);

builder.Host.UseSerilog((ctx, cfg) => cfg.ReadFrom.Configuration(ctx.Configuration));

builder.Services.AddControllers(opt => opt.Filters.Add<CorrelationIdFilter>());
builder.Services.AddMediatR(cfg => cfg.RegisterServicesFromAssemblyContaining<Program>());
builder.Services.AddOpenTelemetry()
    .WithTracing(t => t.AddAspNetCoreInstrumentation().AddHttpClientInstrumentation())
    .WithMetrics(m => m.AddAspNetCoreInstrumentation());

builder.Services.AddRefitClient<IInventoryClient>()
    .ConfigureHttpClient(c => c.BaseAddress = new Uri(builder.Configuration["Services:Inventory"]!))
    .AddPolicyHandler(Policy.TimeoutAsync<HttpResponseMessage>(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(5)))
    .AddPolicyHandler(Policy<HttpResponseMessage>.Handle<HttpRequestException>().CircuitBreakerAsync(5, TimeSpan.FromSeconds(30)));

builder.Services.AddMassTransit(x =>
{
    x.SetKebabCaseEndpointNameFormatter();
    x.AddConsumers(typeof(Program).Assembly);
    x.UsingKafka((ctx, cfg) =>
    {
        cfg.Host("kafka:9092");
        cfg.ConfigureEndpoints(ctx);
    });
});

var app = builder.Build();
app.UseSerilogRequestLogging();
app.MapHealthChecks("/healthz");
app.MapControllers();
app.Run();
```

## 5) Dockerfile (API)
```Dockerfile
FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:9.0 AS base
WORKDIR /app

FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/sdk:9.0 AS build
WORKDIR /src
COPY . .
RUN dotnet restore ./src/Api/Api.csproj
RUN dotnet publish ./src/Api/Api.csproj -c Release -o /app/publish

FROM base AS final
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=build /app/publish .
ENTRYPOINT ["dotnet", "Api.dll"]
```

## 6) docker-compose (Kafka)
```yaml
version: "3.9"
services:
  api:
    build: ..
    environment:
      - ASPNETCORE_URLS=http://+:8080
    ports:
      - "8080:8080"
    depends_on:
      - kafka

  zookeeper:
    image: confluentinc/cp-zookeeper:7.4.0
    environment:
      ZOOKEEPER_CLIENT_PORT: 2181

  kafka:
    image: confluentinc/cp-kafka:7.4.0
    depends_on:
      - zookeeper
    environment:
      KAFKA_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT: zookeeper:2181
      KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS: PLAINTEXT://kafka:9092
      KAFKA_OFFSETS_TOPIC_REPLICATION_FACTOR: 1
    ports:
      - "9092:9092"
```

## 7) Observabilidade
- OTLP exporter para collector central.
- Logs estruturados com traceId e correlation id.
- Health checks em `/healthz` e dependencias (mensageria, DB).

## 8) Resiliencia e confiabilidade
- Polly: timeout, retry com jitter, circuit breaker.
- Idempotencia: chaves de deduplicacao em mensagens e comandos.
- Outbox: persistir eventos de dominio antes de publicar em Kafka.

## 9) Testes
- Unit: handlers MediatR, validators, domain services.
- Integration: subir docker-compose (Kafka) e validar publish/consume; API end-to-end com banco em container.
- Contratos: schemas Avro/JSON para eventos e consumidores.

## 10) Checklist
- Dockerfile e docker-compose presentes.
- Observabilidade ativa (logs + traces + metrics).
- Resiliencia configurada nos HTTP clients e consumers.
- Testes unitarios e de integracao cobrindo fluxos principais e mensageria.
